<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 03:17:00 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>部长称黎巴嫩爆炸中使用的寻呼机部件并非来自台湾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/components-pagers-used-lebanon-blasts-are-not-taiwan-minister-says-2024-09-20/</link><description>台湾经济部长周五表示，周二在黎巴嫩爆炸的数千台寻呼机所使用的部件并非台湾制造。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 02:42:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/components-pagers-used-lebanon-blasts-are-not-taiwan-minister-says-2024-09-20/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲股市沐浴在美联储余辉之中，日元在日本央行之前紧张不安</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-20/</link><description>亚洲股市周五延续涨势，沐浴在美国大幅降息的余辉之中，而日元在日本货币政策决定之前紧张不安，因为交易员寻找未来紧缩政策的线索。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 01:51:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-09-20/</guid></item><item><title>中国出人意料地保持贷款利率稳定；市场预计很快就会降息</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-unexpectedly-leaves-lending-benchmark-lpr-unchanged-2024-09-20/</link><description>中国周五出人意料地将基准贷款利率维持在月度固定利率不变，这与美联储本周早些时候大幅降息后准备采取行动的市场预期相混淆。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 01:07:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-unexpectedly-leaves-lending-benchmark-lpr-unchanged-2024-09-20/</guid></item><item><title>由于供应问题，华为售价 2,800 美元的三折手机上市</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-2800-tri-fold-phone-hits-stores-amid-supply-concerns-2024-09-20/</link><description>华为和苹果的最新智能手机周五在中国上市，这家中国科技公司备受期待的三折叠手机售价为 2,800 美元，价格是 iPhone 16 Pro Max 的两倍多。</description><pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 00:37:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huaweis-2800-tri-fold-phone-hits-stores-amid-supply-concerns-2024-09-20/</guid></item><item><title>拉夫罗夫誓言俄罗斯将捍卫其北极利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/lavrov-vows-russia-defend-its-arctic-interests-2024-09-19/</link><description>俄罗斯外交部长谢尔盖·拉夫罗夫在周五发表的采访中誓言，莫斯科将在外交和军事方面捍卫其在北极的利益。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 23:30:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/lavrov-vows-russia-defend-its-arctic-interests-2024-09-19/</guid></item><item><title>新华社报道，中国和欧洲旨在解决对中国电动汽车调查的分歧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-europe-aim-resolve-differences-over-investigation-chinese-evs-xinhua-2024-09-19/</link><description>新华社周四称，中国商务部部长王文涛和欧盟委员会委员瓦尔迪斯·东布罗夫斯基斯在布鲁塞尔举行的一次会议上表达了解决欧盟对中国电动汽车反补贴调查分歧的政治意愿。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 23:29:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-europe-aim-resolve-differences-over-investigation-chinese-evs-xinhua-2024-09-19/</guid></item><item><title>日本寺庙神社销量激增，打击恶意买家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sales-japan-temples-shrines-surge-crackdown-bad-faith-buyers-2024-09-19/</link><description>铃木本谋 (Benmou Suzuki) 的这座有着 420 年历史的破旧寺庙位于日本一个小山村附近的森林深处，看起来根本不像珍贵的房地产。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 23:14:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/sales-japan-temples-shrines-surge-crackdown-bad-faith-buyers-2024-09-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国贸易代表办公室将对中国多晶硅、硅片、钨关税上调发表评论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/ustr-take-comments-tariff-hikes-chinese-polysilicon-wafers-tungsten-2024-09-19/</link><description>美国贸易代表办公室周四表示，将从周一开始就其对中国多晶硅、硅片和钨产品大幅提高关税的计划接​​受公众意见。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 22:34:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/ustr-take-comments-tariff-hikes-chinese-polysilicon-wafers-tungsten-2024-09-19/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：央行接力棒传递至日本、中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-19/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 21:49:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国销量下滑后梅赛德斯-奔驰再次下调2024年核心利润预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-lowers-annual-core-profit-forecast-after-china-sales-fall-2024-09-19/</link><description>由于中国整体销量下降，梅赛德斯-奔驰周四在不到两个月的时间内第二次下调了全年利润率。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 19:25:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-lowers-annual-core-profit-forecast-after-china-sales-fall-2024-09-19/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟表示，欧盟和中国加大力度避免电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-trade-commissioner-seeking-solution-with-china-over-ev-tariffs-2024-09-19/</link><description>欧盟委员会周四表示，欧盟委员会和中国同意加大力度避免欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收进口关税，并可能重新审查此前被欧盟拒绝的最低价格协议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 17:44:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eus-trade-commissioner-seeking-solution-with-china-over-ev-tariffs-2024-09-19/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议员提议禁止中国企业利用第三国逃避关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/senator-marco-rubio-seeks-bar-chinese-firms-evading-us-tariffs-by-manufacturing-2024-09-19/</link><description>美国共和党参议员马可·卢比奥周四提议禁止中国制造商通过在墨西哥、越南或马来西亚等其他国家设立工厂来逃避关税。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 16:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/senator-marco-rubio-seeks-bar-chinese-firms-evading-us-tariffs-by-manufacturing-2024-09-19/</guid></item><item><title>英国《金融时报》报道，大众汽车对新疆工厂的审核未达到国际标准</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-audit-xinjiang-plant-failed-meet-international-standard-ft-reports-2024-09-19/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周四报道，大众汽车委托对其位于中国新疆的合资工厂进行的审计未能达到该德国汽车制造商审计机构表示为其流程设定的国际标准的关键方面。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:31:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagens-audit-xinjiang-plant-failed-meet-international-standard-ft-reports-2024-09-19/</guid></item><item><title>中国称被指控进入日本海域的航母正在进行例行训练</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-carrier-accused-entering-japanese-waters-was-routine-training-2024-09-19/</link><description>中国周四表示，其辽宁号航母一直在西太平洋执行例行训练任务，并驳回了东京有关该舰及其护航舰进入日本水域的指控。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 11:20:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-carrier-accused-entering-japanese-waters-was-routine-training-2024-09-19/</guid></item><item><title>着眼于经济，斯里兰卡人将在紧张的选举中投票选举总统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/with-eyes-economy-sri-lankans-vote-president-tight-election-2024-09-19/</link><description>预计结果将决定现任总统拉尼尔·维克勒马辛哈领导的脆弱经济复苏的命运。</description><pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 09:22:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/with-eyes-economy-sri-lankans-vote-president-tight-election-2024-09-19/</guid></item></channel></rss>